      "rationale": "Formal use-error analysis (e.g., structured analyst checklist, independent review of simulation setup) is not required at Model Risk Level 2. The absence of pinned configuration parameters in this package increases the practical risk of use error in deployment, but this factor is scoped out at the current MRL."
