    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD predictions of RH are within ±12% of bench measurements across all five COU operating points at the chosen solver settings, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion for the worst-case operating condition. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
